SEC_FILINGS_SEARCH_TOOL_DESCRIPTION = 'This search tool leverages Elasticsearch to comprehensively search across a repository of SEC filings, including 10-K forms and other financial documents. It returns precise matches by analyzing document content, including company names, filing dates, and detailed report information. The tool is designed to extract relevant snippets from documents, highlighting the portions that match the search criteria, and providing quick access to critical financial data, document URLs, and contextual insights into each filing. 10-Ks from the past few years are included for the following ticker symbols: AAPL, MSFT, AMZN, GOOGL, GOOG, META, TSLA, BRK.B, JPM, JNJ. '




